scenes.description: Amelia Watson talks about her birthday and checks her stream recap.
Amelia shares stories about various foods she ate in Japan, including tempura, sushi, and ekibento.
Amelia praises the quality of food in Japan and mentions walking a lot during her trip.
Amelia transitions to looking at a fanbook and some birthday fan art.
Amelia tells a story about eating ramen and the cultural expectation to slurp loudly.
Amelia eats a fruit sando and encourages her viewers to visit Japan for the food.
